    "title": "West Bank suffering its largest displacement crisis since 1967, UN Security Council told",
    "description": "NEW YORK CITY: The West Bank is experiencing its largest displacement crisis since 1967, the UN Security Council heard on Monday. It came as officials and humanitarian agencies warned of an entrenched and unlawful Israeli occupation, while the US accused the world body of ignoring atrocities committed by Hamas against Palestinians in Gaza.",
